Package: geosed
Type: Package
Title: Smallest Enclosing Disc for Latitude and Longitude Points
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-08-17
Author: Shant Sukljian <email@email.com>
Maintainer: Shant Sukljian <email@email.com>
Description: 
    The purpose of the functions in this package is to find the smallest circle that contains all longitude and latitude input points. From the generated center and radius, variable side polygons can be created, navigation based on bearing and distance can be applied, and more.
